Acknowledgements
================================================================================

The system is built around the codified disaster response chain
under the Disaster Management Act 2005 and the operational doctrines
of the National Disaster Management Authority (NDMA), the National
Disaster Response Force (NDRF), the Indian Armed Forces' Aid to
Civil Authority provisions, the National Emergency Response Support
System (112), and the state-level SDRF and SDMA mandates.

